{"title":"风啊，莫再叹息","authors":["安祎"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":10,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"风啊，莫再叹息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安祎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近年来我国西北地区利用风能资源，推广风力发电。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流浪的绝不富有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富有的绝不会流浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你最富有，可谁也说不清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你到底流浪了多少个世纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你叹息，你抽泣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因久久得不到理解；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激愤时也常常慷慨陈词，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"执著的信念，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿破了无数岁月的冰雪雷雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤忱的心愿还得流浪，流浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流浪在无边无涯的天宇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别再对树木发泄了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别再对船只出气了；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一台台风能发电机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在深情地呼唤着——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你奉献，请你给予。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}